text:
1. Prepare mentally and physically
2. Climb to the edge of the cliff
3. Assess the depth and conditions of the water
4. Take a deep breath
5. Jump off the cliff
6. Extend arms and legs outward
7. Maintain a streamlined body position
8. Keep eyes open and focused
9. Rotate body if desired
10. Prepare for impact with the water
11. Enter the water feet-first
12. Maintain control and balance
13. Swim to the surface
14. Assess surroundings and swim to safety if necessary
